name: Glimpses of Rio Collection #001
description: The Glimpses of Rio Collection was designed to be NFT. Each art, totalling 112, brings glimpses of scenes from Rio de Janeiro, extracted from copyrighted photographs by Alexandre Macieira, inviting the viewer to immerse in the set of images. This is the first of the series, establishing itself as the genesis of the project. | www.alexandremacieira.com.br
